w}} ([[BMT Fourth Avenue Line]])\n| Station is [[Americans with Disabilities Act of 1990|ADA-accessible]] in the northbound direction only.\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|alltimes}}\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|limitedrush}}\n| [[Nevins Street (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Nevins Street]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Eastern west|time=show|exclude=4}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|alltimes}}\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|limitedrush}}\n| [[Atlantic Avenue\u2013Barclays Center (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Atlantic Avenue\u2013Barclays Center]]\n| align=center | {{Access icon}}\n| {{NYCS Eastern west|time=show|exclude=4}}<br />{{NYCS Brighton north|time=show}} ([[BMT Brighton Line]])<br />{{NYCS Fourth center|time=show}} ([[BMT Fourth Avenue Line]])\n| [[Long Island Rail Road|LIRR]] [[Atlantic Branch]] at [[Atlantic Terminal (LIRR station)|Atlantic Terminal]]\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|nightsonly}}\n|align=\"center\"|\u2191\n| [[Bergen Street (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Bergen Street]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Eastern west local night|time=show|exclude=4}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|nightsonly}}\n|align=\"center\"|\u2191\n| [[Grand Army Plaza (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Grand Army Plaza]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Eastern west local night|time=show|exclude=4}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|nightsonly}}\n|align=\"center\"|\u2191\n| [[Eastern Parkway\u2013Brooklyn Museum (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Eastern Parkway\u2013Brooklyn Museum]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Eastern west local night|time=show|exclude=4}}\n|\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|alltimes}}\n| align=center | {{NYCS SSI|limitedrush}}\n| [[Franklin Avenue (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Franklin Avenue]]\n|\n| {{NYCS Eastern west|time=show|exclude=4}}<br />{{NYCS Franklin|time=show}} ([[BMT Franklin Avenue Line]])\n|\n|-\n| align=center colspan=2 | {{NYCS SSI|nightsonly}}\n|align=\"center\"|\u2191\n| [[Nostrand Avenue (IRT Eastern Parkway Line)|Nostrand Avenue]]\n|\n|\n| [[B44 SBS (New Y